node.text:
Thank you @netflix for letting me take my shirt off in front of millions of people.  My mom would be proud!  #blingempire 
-

Let’s go #asian representation in all forms of media!!! Now in #realitytv 
-
Thank you to @jeffreycjenkins , this wouldn’t have been possible if you didn’t think I was ripped enough. 
-
Thank you @brandonpanaligan and @really_tall_ryan  you two were amazing to be with the last two years!
-
And thank you to all my cast mates.  I’m sorry ahead of time @kellymili @kanelk_k @christine_chiu88 @jaimexie @cherieofficial @kimlee @guy_tang @

node.text: When I’m not speaking as an advocate for equality, I’m doing my other job and passion...fitness coaching.  I retired from personal training this December and not taking on anymore future clients...but I am taking on coaching clients and collaborating with awesome folks like Guy help inspire others to take control of the physical, mental, and spiritual health.

node.text: Personal message

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kevin Kreider on August 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Having a #sober lifestyle has its downfalls of sleeping better, thinking different, having more time to pursue your dreams, and no empty calories so you may get a six pack.  Oh, and more $ in your bank account.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kevin Kreider on August 16, 2021 tagging @areaanational. May be an image of 1 person, beard, sitting and indoor.

node.text: Living life in my most honest expression

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kevin Kreider on August 13, 2021 tagging @somlit_. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: For growth there’s always a few steps forward, one step back.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kevin Kreider on August 11, 2021 tagging @k29style. May be an image of 1 person, beard and indoor.

node.text: Want abs while lying around?  Buy my matcha.  Actually, you won’t get abs with matcha and lying around, but you’ll get access to my free online course that will help you when you buy the matcha for the first time.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kevin Kreider on August 09, 2021 tagging @somlit_. May be an image of 1 person, biceps, standing, activewear and footwear.

node.text: Leaning into gratitude

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kevin Kreider on August 06, 2021 tagging @k29style. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text: Coffee or matcha?  I do love both, coffee helps with my #intermittentfasting lifestyle and matcha helps with my smooth focus and antioxidants #MatchaMantra

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kevin Kreider on August 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, beard and indoor.

node.text: Being Korean adopted, I get the best of both worlds
